{"tid":641735,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中大白象 - 有汗出冇糧出","createTime":"2018-04-25T08:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T08:25:36.000Z","uid":12929,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c41b400969468ac2b7771a0c71e85d50c11ac9","tid":641735,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>港鐵沙中綫紅磡站工程分判商</strong>，去年4月至6月連續<strong>拖欠6名員工合共約46萬元薪金</strong>，被票控18項欠薪罪名。公司早前不認罪受審，辯稱大判因應社會不滿工程延誤，催促分判商增加人手趕工，但<strong>因立法會拉布，公司只獲很少撥款，終周轉不靈無錢發薪</strong>。裁判官今指，案發時公司的銀行結存為負債180萬元，根本<strong>無法出糧</strong>，<strong>構成合理辯解</strong>，裁定<strong>全部罪名不成立</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官裁決指，被告碧海土木工程有限公司在案發期間，各銀行戶口即使有正數結餘，也因轉賬至發薪系統，數天之間存款插水至負數百多萬，不能排除被告是用結餘先向其他員工發薪，才<strong>逼不得已犯案</strong>。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180425/58116716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58116716&d=S8c6LNgzw8aMKwOJUYsK67ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c5e11309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58116716&h=18147f95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180425/58116716</a>"}]}